    "BERN2 can be implemented through their RESTFUL API [46].",
    "For each sentence, BERN2 produces a JSON list of annotations, containing the entity phrase, its entity type, and a probability score.",
    "Sentences are eliminated if the annotation list contains fewer than two gene/protein entities.",
    "In Stage-2 of GIX, we used BERN2 for NER and fine-tuned BioBERT for relation classification.",
    "Through fine-tuning on expert-annotated data, pre-trained models efficiently transfer general language knowledge to domain-specific tasks, resulting in improved task performance and adaptability."
